OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773129873
OL,3,C'He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,4,Cme and made me live in fear'
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 14 years
OL,7,Fafter being found guilty of
OL,8,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour and
OL,9,Fattempted rape in Wirral.
OL,11,FDamien Lang, 41 years, of Heyes Drive
OL,12,Fin Leasowe appeared at Liverpool Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Friday 6 March and was
OL,14,Fsentenced to 14 years in prison and
OL,15,Feight years on extended licence.
OL,17,FHe was also issued with an an
OL,18,Findefinite restraining order not to
OL,19,Fcontact the victim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
