FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773129873
OL,3,C'He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,4,Cme and made me live in fear'
OL,6,FThis sentencing relates to domestic
OL,7,Fcrimes against a female victim over a
OL,8,Fthree-year period with a former
OL,9,Fpartner.
OL,11,FLang was subsequently charged in
OL,12,FFebruary last year and in January this
OL,13,Fyear he was found guilty of
OL,14,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour and
OL,15,Fattempted rape.
OL,17,FIn a victim impact statement read out
OL,18,Fin court, she said: "The abuse I
OL,19,Fsuffered has left me traumatised in
OL,20,Fways I still struggle to put into
OL,21,Fwords.
OL,26,@zD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773129873
OL,3,C'He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,4,Cme and made me live in fear'
OL,6,F"He was someone I trusted, someone who
OL,7,Fmanipulated me into love by pretending
OL,8,Fto be someone he wasn't.
OL,10,F"He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,11,Fme and made me live in fear. Even now,
OL,12,Flong after it's over I don't feel safe
OL,13,Fand what he did changed my life
OL,14,Fforever.
OL,16,F"What's worse is that he normalised
OL,17,Feverything bad he did to me and made
OL,18,Fme believe that it was part of a
OL,19,Frelationship ` that it was somehow my
OL,20,Ffault and I was overreacting.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773129873
OL,3,C'He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,4,Cme and made me live in fear'
OL,6,F"Over time I stopped trusting my own
OL,7,Finstincts and I began to doubt myself
OL,8,Fand accept pain as normal ` that kind
OL,9,Fof emotional manipulation stayed with
OL,10,Fme long after the relationship ended.
OL,12,F"This has affected every area of my
OL,13,Flife. I no longer trust people,
OL,14,Fespecially men. I avoid relationships
OL,15,Fand feel disconnected with the world
OL,16,Faround me. The emotional damage is
OL,17,Fdeep and ongoing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773129873
OL,3,C'He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,4,Cme and made me live in fear'
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Holly Chance said:
OL,7,F"Lang put his victim through the
OL,8,Ftrauma of having to relive the
OL,9,Fexperience by way of a trial, but
OL,10,Fthankfully a jury saw through his lies
OL,11,Fand he is now paying for his crimes.
OL,13,F"While no sentence will repair the
OL,14,Fdamage he inflicted on his victim, I
OL,15,Fhope this conviction has secured some
OL,16,Fjustice for her. I would like to
OL,17,Fpraise the courage, strength and
OL,18,Fdignity shown by the victim throughout
OL,19,Fthe case and would like to ask for
OL,20,Fanyone else suffering from similar to
OL,21,Fcome forward.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773129873
OL,3,C'He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,4,Cme and made me live in fear'
OL,6,F"This result shows that violence
OL,7,Fagainst women and girls will simply
OL,8,Fnot be tolerated and we will work
OL,9,Ftirelessly to bring perpetrators to
OL,10,Fjustice."
OL,12,FDet Insp Chance added: "I would like
OL,13,Fto emphasise that there is plenty of
OL,14,Fhelp available to anyone who may be
OL,15,Fsuffering domestic abuse of any kind
OL,16,Fand together with partner agencies, we
OL,17,Fwill do all that we can to support you.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]tD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
