OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773129873
OL,3,C'He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,4,Cme and made me live in fear'
OL,6,F"Domestic abuse can happen to anyone
OL,7,Fand we have specially trained officers
OL,8,Fwho will listen to you and support you
OL,9,Fwith sensitivity and compassion.
OL,11,F"Likewise, I would ask everyone to
OL,12,Flook out for your family members,
OL,13,Ffriends or neighbours that may be
OL,14,Fsuffering, as by contacting us you
OL,15,Fcould be helping someone who is too
OL,16,Fafraid to help themselves.
OL,18,F"Everything you tell us is taken
OL,19,Fextremely seriously and will be
OL,20,Finvestigated thoroughly."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
