OL,3,C'He controlled me, hurt me, threatened
OL,4,Cme and made me live in fear'
OL,6,FMerseyside Police have launched a
OL,7,FViolence against Women and Girls
OL,8,F(VAWG) campaign to put the voices of
OL,9,Fwomen and girls at the heart of their
OL,10,Fwork to keep them safe.
OL,12,FPartners can also request information
OL,13,Funder Clare's Law, the Domestic
OL,14,FViolence Disclosure Scheme. This
OL,15,Fscheme enables the police to release
OL,16,Finformation about any previous history
OL,17,Fof violence or abuse a person might
OL,18,Fhave.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
